items.name: Tumhain Dillagi Bhool Jani Paray Gi
Bujhi Hui Shama Ka Dhuan Hoon
Sohne Mukhre Da Lain De Nazara
Sehar Qarib Hai Taron Ka Hal Kya Ho Ga
Wadah Kar Ke Sajjan Nahee Aya
Ganj Shakr Ke Naam Ka Sadqa
Rabba Kadi Vi Na Paen Vichore
Main Kahin Bhi Jaon Eh Jaan
Meri Shutar Sawara Gal Sun Ja
Meri Bhi Suno Sab Ke Dukh Dard
Changi Aan Mandan Aan Sahib Teri
Is Karam Ka Karon Shukar Kaise Ada
Meri Bukkal De Vich Chor Chor
Hum Hosh Bhi Apne Bhool Gaye
